Class HomeController

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
javafx.scene.Parent
javafx.scene.layout.Region

javafx.scene.control.Labeled
javafx.scene.control.Label
controllers.HomeController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget, javafx.fxml.Initializable, javafx.scene.control.Skinnable
public class HomeController
extends javafx.scene.control.Label
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
The type Home controller. The HomeController class contains general methods related to the broader application. It controls the Home.fxml page. The HomeController class acts as a primary router and may call on other controller classes to complete actions when necessary.
